{SECT 0 {PARA 256 "" 0 "" {TEXT 257 23 "Algebraic Manipulations" }}
{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 13 "Lue Jane King" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 
-1 15 "April 6th, 2003" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 179 "Save your curr
ent worksheet as work02-yourlastname.mws.  Remember to save frequently
 to avoid losing data in case that the system would shut down in the m
iddle of a work session! " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "
" 0 "" {TEXT -1 104 "In the text mode (click on the cap T button) plac
e your name(s) and date at the top of your worksheet.  " }}{PARA 0 "" 
0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 531 "1.  Basic Manipulat
ions.  We can use Maple to manipulate algebraic expression as well as \+
to perform arithmetic calculations.  The intent is to learn some basic
 Maple syntax, while observing some of the neat features of a Computer
 Algebra System (CAS).  We will also review some basic concepts from a
rithmetic.   Perform the following calculations with Maple.  As you do
 these exercises enter notes and comments onto your worksheet in text \+
mode.  Note the usage of operators +,-,*,/,^,!  and the usage or non-u
sage of parentheses.  " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 
0 "" {TEXT -1 60 "Let the following variables represent algebraic expr
essions:" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 
6 "1.    " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "f := x^3-x^2-2*x" "6#>%\"fG,(*$%\"xG\"\"$\"
\"\"*$F'\"\"#!\"\"*&F+F)F'F)F," }{TEXT -1 11 "      2.   " }{XPPEDIT 
19 1 "g := 6*x^3+11*x^2+6*x+1" "6#>%\"gG,**&\"\"'\"\"\"*$%\"xG\"\"$F(F
(*&\"#6F(*$F*\"\"#F(F(*&F'F(F*F(F(F(F(" }{TEXT -1 22 "                \+
 3.   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "h := x^3-5*x+x^2-5;" "6#>%\"hG,**$%\"xG\"\"$\"
\"\"*&\"\"&F)F'F)!\"\"*$F'\"\"#F)F+F," }{TEXT -1 19 "                 \+
  " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 6 "4.    " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "F := x^4-1" 
"6#>%\"FG,&*$%\"xG\"\"%\"\"\"F)!\"\"" }{TEXT -1 22 "                5.
    " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "G := 3*x^4+4*x^3-2*x^2+x-6;" "6#>%\"GG,,*&\"\"$
\"\"\"*$%\"xG\"\"%F(F(*&F+F(*$F*F'F(F(*&\"\"#F(*$F*F/F(!\"\"F*F(\"\"'F
1" }{TEXT -1 14 "         6.   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "H := 2*x^2+3*x-2" "6#
>%\"HG,(*&\"\"#\"\"\"*$%\"xGF'F(F(*&\"\"$F(F*F(F(F'!\"\"" }{TEXT -1 
24 "                        " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 
0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 49 "Calcuate the following (each on a separate line
):" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 9 "a.  \+
